{"tid":2403713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾傳銷狗","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T02:31:11.000Z","uid":370786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"906311d8f3a0e3faff676ea84a28e28a0397796b","tid":2403713,"uid":370786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"記得唔好好心幫人填問卷啦 <br />\n賣哂你啲資料比人啊"},{"pid":"1e61e8abc8f67ffebcb34f3dcc97d8fd831be7d8","tid":2403713,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=bcb22dc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=4fb0eb4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=46e22772\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b61a041ee688cabc3269d362713812bd219dc5a3","tid":2403713,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你可以聽下d錄音，有佢哋點呃人嘅手法<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uBd2Ja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uBd2Ja.png&h=5fe1a552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騙徒Crystal Li李婉瑩新電話號碼: <span class=\"red\">91570141</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cMOhAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cMOhAV.jpg&h=0de4aa7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTyg7Fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTyg7Fc.jpg&h=9f46bf9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">更多資訊： </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=b3566f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=80caeb04\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n<span class=\"red\">常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) </span><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢部分冇p圖嘅真樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5DLuR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5DLuR6.jpg&h=b894d392&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOkHOCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOkHOCZ.jpg&h=f279000e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mSK1X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mSK1X0.jpg&h=be2c20d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係條女部分聲音 Backup <br />\n<br />\n同人plan 升學路線? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-24&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=d25c50ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24</a> <br />\n<br />\n想叫我個fd上去 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoun